title: Tom Clancys Rainbow Six - Vegas 2
description:
No Passwords. No Viruses. No Trojans. No Rubbish.


If you enjoy this game then please seed.



Tom Clancy&#039;s Rainbow Six Vegas 2 is the last chance for gamers to rescue 
America&#039;s sexiest city from an escalating terrorist siege that will impose 
heart-pounding action from beginning to end. The best are back and this 
time winner takes all. The highly-anticipated sequel to the recipient of 
numerous awards, including 2006&#039;s Best First Person Shooter and Best 
Online Game, Tom Clancy&#039;s Rainbow Six Vegas 2 will push the top-selling 
franchise to new heights with new gameplay features and groundbreaking 
co-op and multiplayer modes.
